title: Harvey and Murphy lead Mets over Cubs 4-2 in NLCS opener
text:
> Sports Harvey and Murphy lead Mets over Cubs 4-2 in NLCS opener New York Mets pitcher Matt Harvey reacts after getting Chicago Cubs' Tommy La Stella to strike out during the seventh inning of Game 1 of the National League baseball championship series Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015, in New York.
